          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "In production API environments, managing FLUX.2 Klein 4B BF16 latency is essential for maintaining low response times and high throughput. This model, optimized with BF16 precision, offers a balance between performance and resource efficiency, but latency can vary based on deployment choices. This guide provides actionable insights for API teams to fine-tune latency in real-world scenarios."
