      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To reduce latency, focus on practical optimizations: tune batch sizes based on hardware limits, enable model quantization beyond BF16 if supported, and implement caching for frequent queries. Additionally, use asynchronous processing and load balancing to distribute requests efficiently. The table below summarizes common techniques and their typical impact:"
