            "type": "text",
            "text": "Establish baseline latency metrics through benchmarking tools such as Apache Bench or custom scripts that simulate API traffic. Monitor key indicators like p95 latency, throughput, and error rates using observability platforms (e.g., Prometheus, Grafana). Regularly test under varying loads to detect regressions, and automate alerts for latency spikes. This proactive approach ensures sustained performance as traffic scales or model updates are deployed."
